    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次十幢菩薩本界佛南無東方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙寶世界無盡幢佛金剛幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無南方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙樂世界風幢佛堅固幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無西方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙銀世界解脫幢佛勇猛幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無北方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙金世界威儀幢佛光明幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無東南方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙摩尼世界明相幢佛智幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無西南方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙金剛世界常幢佛寶幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無西北方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙波頭摩世界最勝幢佛精進幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無東北方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙優鉢羅世界自在幢佛離垢幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無下方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙栴檀世界梵幢佛星宿幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾南無上方萬佛剎微塵數剎土外妙香世界觀察幢佛法幢菩薩萬佛剎微塵數道場一切海眾至心歸命禮大方廣佛華嚴經華藏世界海本尊毗盧遮那佛　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中南無大方廣佛華嚴經中華藏世界海十身無礙本尊毗盧遮那佛南無十身無礙毗盧遮那如來道場一切海眾南無大方廣佛華嚴經中十迴向品法門　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中十迴向品第二十五經云爾時金剛幢菩薩(至)入此三昧善根力故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0256c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次護助佛南無如是等十方各過無量無盡無等佛剎微塵數同名金剛幢一切諸佛　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云爾時諸佛各以右手(至)普賢菩薩行願器故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257a19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中十迴向品之餘經云佛子菩薩摩訶薩(至)普令眾生究竟皆得。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257b02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中　　　十迴向品之餘經云佛子菩薩摩訶薩(至)令於實法正思惟。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257b05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中　　　十迴向品之餘經云佛子云何為菩薩(至)皆得清淨到於彼岸。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次該攝果海十迴向法門南無為法界第一迴向菩薩救護一切眾生離眾生相迴向法門南無為法界第二迴向菩薩不壞迴向法門南無為法界第三迴向菩薩等一切諸佛迴向法門南無為法界第四迴向菩薩至一切處迴向法門南無為法界第五迴向菩薩無盡功德藏迴向法門南無為法界第六迴向菩薩入一切平等善根迴向法門南無為法界第七迴向菩薩等隨順一切眾生迴向法門南無為法界第八迴向菩薩真如相迴向法門南無為法界第九迴向菩薩無縛無著解脫迴向法門南無為法界第十迴向菩薩入法界無量迴向法門　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云爾時佛神力故(至)兜率天宮悉亦如是。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次瑞相分中一切諸天南無阿僧祇諸天身無量百千億不可說天妙法音不可思議天讚佛音阿僧祇天歡喜音咸稱善哉諸天一切海眾南無無量阿僧祇百千億那由他諸天恭敬禮拜無數天子常念諸佛希求如來無量功德心不捨離無數天子作眾伎樂歌咏讚歎供養如來一切諸天海眾南無如是等不可說不可說十方三世盡虗空遍法界一切佛剎現無量阿僧祇諸佛境界如來化身出過諸天一切諸天海眾　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中經云爾時復以佛神力故(至)所住行願無能量。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257c06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　願共諸眾生　　往生華藏海　　極樂淨土中次法界兜率證法佛南無十方過十億佛剎微塵數世界外有百萬佛剎微塵數金剛光世界中金剛幢一切諸佛次證法菩薩南無十方十億佛剎微塵數世界外有百萬佛剎微塵數金剛光世界中百萬佛剎微塵數金剛幢菩薩一切海眾次法界兜率天宮十迴向菩薩南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住救護眾生離眾生相迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住不壞迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住等一切諸佛迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住至一切處迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住無盡功德藏迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住隨順一切善根堅固迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住隨順平等一切眾生迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住真如相迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中住無縛無著解脫迴向位菩薩一切海眾南無十方三世盡虗空界微塵剎土中於入無量法界迴向位菩薩一切海眾至心歸命禮大方廣佛華嚴經中華藏世界海本尊毗盧遮那佛　十方盡歸命　　滅罪增淨信　　願生華藏海　極樂淨土中次法界橫死孤魂罪報懺悔惟願帝網無盡佛法僧寶。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0257c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毗盧遮那如來。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "普賢文殊海會聖眾。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出世出神。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "慈悲本願。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "放大光明。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "炤於法會。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "證明護念。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "哀憫攝受。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願我及一切眾生海。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自從無始。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b09_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "直至今時。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "業海無盡。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "帝網重重。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "天地虗曠。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三界四府。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苦中極苦。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無救無依。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非所見聞。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有橫死孤魂罪報。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發露懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼中橫死者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大涅槃經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "死有三種。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一破戒死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二放逸死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三命盡死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有九種橫死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛告比丘。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有九輩九因緣命未盡便橫死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者為不應飯而飯。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者為不量飯。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者為不習飯。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者為不出生。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b16_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者為生熱。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者為不持五戒。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者為近惡知識。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者入里不時不如法行。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者為避罪報不避因死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "罪報懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又藥師經云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時阿難問救脫菩薩言。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何已盡之命而可增益。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "救脫菩薩言。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大德。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝豈不聞如來說有九橫死耶。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故勸造續命旛燈。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "修諸福德。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以修福故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "盡其壽命。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b22_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不經苦患。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "阿難問言。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九橫云何。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "救脫菩薩言。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b22_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸有情得病雖輕。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然無醫藥及看病者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "設復遇毉。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "授以非藥。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "實不應死而便橫死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又信世間邪魔外道妖孽之師妄說禍福。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便生恐動。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不自正。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "卜問覓禍。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "殺種種眾生。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "解奏神明。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "呼諸魍魎。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "請乞福祐。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲冀延年終不能得。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚癡迷惑。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "信邪倒見。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遂令橫死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "入於地獄。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有出期。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名初橫。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者橫被王法之所誅戮。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者畋獵嬉戲。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "躭婬嗜酒。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "放逸無度。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "橫為非人奪其精氣。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者橫為火焚。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五者橫為水溺。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六者橫為種種惡獸所噉。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c06_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七者橫墮山崖。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c07_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "八者橫為毒藥魘禱呪詛起屍鬼等之所中害。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c07_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "九者饑渴所困不得飲食。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c08_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而便橫死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c09_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為如來略說橫死有此九種。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c09_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其餘復有無量諸橫難可具說。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c09_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "罪報懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c10_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又瑜伽師地論云。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "死有三種。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂壽盡故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "福盡故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不避不平等故。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知亦是時非時死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或由善心。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或不善心。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或無記心。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何壽盡故死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如有一隨感。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "壽量滿盡故死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此名時死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何福盡故死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶如有一資具闕故死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何不避不平等故死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c15_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如世尊說九因九緣未盡壽量而死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c15_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為九。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂食無度量。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "食時不宜。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不消復食。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生而不吐。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "熟而持之。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不近醫藥。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知於己。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c17_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若損若益。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c17_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非時非量。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行非梵行。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此名非時死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c18_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何善心死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c18_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "人命將終。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c18_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自憶先時所習善法。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c19_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或因他人提撕。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c19_24",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃能憶念。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c19_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此因緣。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c20_26",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時信等善法現行於心。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c20_27",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為善心死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c20_28",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何為無記心死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人曾習善法。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "臨終不能憶。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又無他人提撕令憶。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為無記心死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何不善心死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人命將終。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自憶先時串習惡法。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或復由他人引起憶念。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼於爾時。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "貪嗔癡諸不善法現行於心。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至麤細等想。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0258c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "現行於前。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為不善心死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又善心死時。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "安樂而死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "惡心死時。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸苦逼迫於身。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "苦惱而死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又善心死者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a02_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不見亂色相。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不善心死者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "見亂色相。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無記心死者。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a03_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "昏懵不惺。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖非苦惱死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "亦非安樂死。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "罪報懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又法界面然鬼王所統。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "薜茘多部百億河沙餓鬼。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "非我見聞。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a05_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有名無名塵沙種族人間。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "依於草木。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "附彼城隍。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "銜冤魂識。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "品物精靈。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自殘自盡。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無依無托。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "遺骸暴骨。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乏祭餒魂。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "魑魅魍魎。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有三財九品一切幽魂。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "罪報懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸佛子等。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "為無明所覆。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不識罪因。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今遇道場。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "方能覺知。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "歸命毗盧遮那如來。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a11_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及一切賢聖海眾。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燒香散花。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "橫死孤魂所受罪業。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發露懺悔。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不敢覆藏。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此因緣。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法界眾生海。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "橫死孤魂一切罪報。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉願清淨。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次懺悔滅罪印呪",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唵薩栗末(二合)巴(引)巴眉悉普怛[口*捺]曷捺末日囉也莎曷(應誦三徧)　百劫積集罪　　一念悉盪除　　如火焚枯草　滅盡無有餘　我昔所造諸惡業　　皆由無始貪瞋癡　從身語意之所生　　一切我今皆懺悔懺悔已。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至心歸命禮本尊毗盧遮那佛。",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "○(白)眾等聽說經中無常偈",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　上至非非想　　下至轉輪王　　七寶鎮隨身　千子常圍繞　　如其壽命盡　　須臾不暫停　還漂生死海　　隨緣受眾苦大方廣佛華嚴經海印道場十重行願常徧禮懺儀卷第二十二",
        "from": "X74n1470_022:0259a23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]